prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hilariously attempting to blow out a single, very determined candle on a small cupcake that it's holding. The sloth has a look of comical concentration, with puffed-out cheeks. The text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script in the center. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, pastel colors, visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and cupcake, giving it a whimsical, hand-painted feel.
